---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Disclaimer — IMTI" description="SEBI-compliant investment disclaimer">
  <div class="card" style="max-width:800px;">
    <h1 style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:16px;">Investment Disclaimer</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:24px;">Last updated: April 23, 2026</p>

    <div style="background:rgba(248,81,73,0.1);padding:16px;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid var(--accent-red);margin-bottom:24px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--accent-red);">⚠️ NOT INVESTMENT ADVICE</h2>
      <p style="font-size:13px;">The India Market Timing Index (IMTI) and all associated content are strictly for <strong>educational and informational purposes</strong>. This is NOT investment advice, and we are NOT SEBI-registered Investment Advisers or Research Analysts.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">1. No Registration</h2>
    <p>IMTI is not registered with the Securities and Exchange Board of India (SEBI) under the SEBI (Investment Advisers) Regulations, 2013, or the SEBI (Research Analysts) Regulations, 2014. We do not provide personalized investment advice.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">2. Risk Disclosure</h2>
    <p>Investing in securities involves substantial risk, including the possible loss of principal. The use of leverage (MTF/Pay-Later) amplifies both gains and losses. A 10% decline in a 3x leveraged position results in a 30% loss of capital.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">3. No Guarantees</h2>
    <p>We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of any data, scores, or recommendations. Market data is sourced from third-party providers (yfinance, NSE, etc.) and may be delayed or incorrect.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">4. Past Performance</h2>
    <p>Backtests and historical results shown on this site are hypothetical. Past performance is NOT indicative of future results. The IMTI scoring system has not been tested in live markets over extended periods.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">5. User Responsibility</h2>
    <p>You are solely responsible for your investment decisions. Always consult a SEBI-registered Investment Adviser before making investment decisions. Do not rely solely on IMTI data.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">6. Conflicts of Interest</h2>
    <p>The creators of IMTI may hold positions in stocks discussed on this site. We do not receive compensation from any company for featuring their stock. The site is funded through display advertising.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">7. Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions, email <a href="mailto:support@imti.in">support@imti.in</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
